    "details": [
      {
        "title": "Native Audio Integration",
        "description": "Wan 2.5 takes video generation to the next level by natively rendering visuals with organically produced audio, directly from descriptive prompts. From ambient effects to background music, the Wan 2.5 AI video model ensures users no longer need extra editing tools or third-party software to create full videos with synchronized sounds.",
