      {
        "title": "What is Wan 2.5?",
        "description": "Wan 2.5 is the latest addition to the Wan AI model family. Capable of text-to-video and image-to-video generation, this release brings significant upgrades to help creators produce more dynamic visual scenes with greater scene complexity and character detail."
      },
      {
        "title": "What makes Wan 2.5 AI video model better than Wan 2.2?",
        "description": "Compared to Wan 2.2, this new AI video model better simulates real-world character motion, while maintaining style consistency and visual fidelity across scenes. This, paired with its native audio generation capabilities and rapid video rendering, makes it even more suited to creative storytelling."
      },
      {
        "title": "Can I access the Wan 2.5 AI video model for free?",
        "description": "Absolutely. Using Veo3 AI, you can start using the Wan 2.5 model to generate videos at no cost via our free trial plan. Just keep in mind that it only offers limited credits, so if you want to keep creating, then you will eventually need a paid plan."
      },
      {
        "title": "Best practices for prompting on Wan 2.5 AI video model?",
        "description": "Wan 2.5 comes with enhanced semantic understanding, which lets it intuitively understand your instructions and generate detailed visual sequences more accurately. With less reiteration needed, you don’t need to use overly complex sentences. Instead, just be direct when describing the scene and also try to avoid any conflicting instructions."
      },
      {
        "title": "How does the audio feature of Wan 2.5 AI video model work?",
        "description": "You have two options. The AI can automatically generate a suitable soundtrack or sound effects for your video based on your video. You can also upload your own audio or video file to extract the audio tracks (like music or a voiceover) for your video."
      }
